text:
I'm make studies in communication but my dream is to make a career in basketball. I want to be a scout to evaluate differents players for recruiting good for many teams, but I can also be an assistant coach, or many a coach. Everything is possible like Alex Dupont said. That's my goal and I work everyday on that to become everytime better. This summer I'm going to travel in Paris to watch the world cup u19. The goal of that travel is to watch in real life many of the biggest basketball prospects. I'm work also with Envergure, this is a group of people, who are passionated with the goal of share this passion with many people. So, I write article or make video to explain the game of many young players. One of my inspiration is a member of this group, who is actualy assistant coach for the basketball team of the university of Santa Clara in Paris. He's six or seven years older than me and he had the same start of cursus. So, with many work, I think it's possible for me to follow his step to work in that field. He put hardwork from many years so I try to do the same thinks, that's give me some motivation to work harder. The goal is to grind one percent each day to be the best as possible. That's why, he and many other people who's older than me inspirate myself to be the best person as possible and to make the best work as possible to simply be one of the best in my way.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will recordeach time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data isstored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the produced data are available here.
